data.description: Come on out and tour this recently remodeled 3 Bedroom 2 Bath home located in Palo Alto Village. This home features a new roof,  new AC , new flooring, and updated kitchen, updated restrooms and updated electrical. This home  has a spacious open floor plan and a large back yard to host your gatherings. Conveniently located near highway 16, and Palo Alto Rd. just minutes from Texas A&M San Antonio, Palo Alto college and Toyota Manufacturing Plant. Schedule your showing today!
